review:
I love this app and use it to listen to all of my favorite songs, stations, and playlists. However, there is a slight bug when listening to music and reading the extended lyric menu;

When you scroll through the lyrics, the three bars signifying a large break between lines will not move unless you actively move through the menu, and the second count becomes inactive while you do so...

This bug has no effect on the overall performance of the app, but is just a small glitch that has been noticed. I would definitely recommend this app to anyone looking for a high-quality, add free experience.

